breaking news is a 2012 kannada satirical comedy film directed , written and produced by nagathihalli chandrashekar . it stars ajay rao and radhika pandit in the lead roles while actor ananth nag makes a special appearance . stephen &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; is the music director and krishna kumar is the cinematographer of the film . the film got its theatrical release on 18 may 2012 .